    name: "Tank does donuts amid armed conflict in Ukraine",
    long_name: null,
    description: "###*Is this video WTF? Rank it.* The situation in Ukraine right now is not good. That is putting things mildly. Tensions are running high in the armed conflict between pro-Russia and opposition forces. Still, there was a brief moment of levity in the eastern Ukranian city of Sloviansk. A tank belonging to pro-Russian forces decided to do some donuts before speeding away. Wonder if that tank driver needed [a push-button line lock feature][1]. ###*What do you think of this tank burnout? Tell us in the Comments.* [1]: http://www.networka.com/videos/29773/2015-ford-mustang-gt-has-line-lock-feature-for-burnouts",
