    featured_at: null,
    slug: "drifter-niculae-dobre-only-uses-one-hand-to-drift",
    attribution_id: 641,
    sponsor_id: null,
    picture_id: 32223,
    provider: "YouTube",
    provider_description: "You just know there's something special with this guy from the moment you see him driving. The levels of commitment and involvement are absolutely off the chart! His name is Dobre, his car is a V8 powered BMW E30, and he drifts using just one hand! Oh, and we were in the middle of a tandem with Marius KNS the whole time! Uber cool! More drifting news,videos and photos can be seen on : www.facebook.com/drift.ro Please subscribe to the channel and also like our Facebook page! http://www.youtube.com/user/driftshorts",
